OL,7,F"With the freezing of tax rate bands,
OL,8,Fwhat will the two per cent cut in
OL,9,FNational Insurance mean for average
OL,10,Fearnings?" says Howard Smith of Luton
OL,12,FThe earnings threshold when you start
OL,13,Fto pay National Insurance is #12,570 -
OL,14,F#242 a week. Up to that level you
OL,15,Fdon't pay it.
OL,17,FIt's in sync with the earnings
OL,18,Fthreshold for income tax but it has
OL,19,Fnot risen in sync with inflation and
OL,20,Faverage earnings.
