OL,7,FIt's been calculated if that threshold
OL,8,Fhad gone up with prices you would now
OL,9,Fbe out of tax and National Insurance
OL,10,Fif you earn up to #15,00...which would
OL,11,Ftake some low earners out of tax.
OL,13,FBut the existing threshold for
OL,14,FNational Insurance and other taxes is
OL,15,Fset to be frozen until 2028 (it last
OL,16,Fwent up in 2022), by which time it
OL,17,Fwill be earning the Treasury an extra
OL,18,F#29 billion a year. This is why some
OL,19,Fpeople call it a stealth task.
