OL,7,FNow, Carys will be helped by a change
OL,8,Fthat's been made.
OL,10,FPreviously, if either parent earned
OL,11,Fmore than #50k a year they would have
OL,12,Fhad to pay back some or all of their
OL,13,Fchild benefit. That's been pushed up
OL,14,Fto #60k from April.
